<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>27</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pa'n vangphatna piek di'n ei ngak,
 A Thagau thilbawl theihna'n;
 En mah diu, vangsakna guohpi,
 Hung zu dingin a kisa'i.

[V2]
 Hun sawl in aw Pa, ka ngen ui,
 Na vangphatna guohpi chu;
 Ka ngak ui, ka ngak zing zieng ui,
 Ka lung sung uh hihhalh in.

[V3]
 2. Pathien a um tih I heu ui,
 I kawm ah A um zing hi;
 Mahleh A halhna I ngai ui,
 A lungsietna manbei chu.

[V4]
 3. Pathien a um chu I ging ui,
 I dahnau cheng tun hitiu;
 A hehpihna'n ei sang ina,
 A mi khawtuoh theih ziekin.

[V5]
 4. I pauchamnau Ama'n A sang,
 Ginna mawlpen himah leng;
 A hehpihna'n ei phawng ding hi,
 Gitloh a puksa nungte.</lyrics>
<title>REVIVE THE HEARTS OF ALL</title>
</song>